description: For 15 years Donaven's amazed and delighted The city of Tallahassee with it's great service and food, and now it's come back in an all new way with Donaven's Road Cookin! Southern food with an Irish style, you won't find food like this anywhere else. Irish Sausage Rolls, Double Dublin Dogs, Irish Breakfast Wraps, and more are here for you at Donaven's Road Cookin!
name: Donaven's Road Cookin
